platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Well take any excuse to visit Deus Exs techno dystopia, but experiencing it as a turn-based puzzler is a true delight. What amazes us most is how Deus Ex GO re-creates the action-RPG series trademark features while preserving the stunning visuals and clever strategy of Lara Croft GO and Hitman GO. We got chills stomping guards with vicious takedowns and altering levels by hacking them. Theres even an intriguing story (pitting Adam Jensen against heavily armed terrorists) to keep you going.
